Single transaction:
python -m src.predict --amount 1000000 --type "TRANSFER"

Output:
{
  "amount": 1000000,
  "type": "TRANSFER",
  "prediction": "fraud",
  "probability": 0.97
}

Batch CSV:
python -m src.predict --csv data/raw/AML_Fraud_full.csv
AML_Fraud_full_predictions.csv is created next to the input file
